Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.48,0:00:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The most crucial moment in life is during decision making.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.36,0:00:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pacific War taught us the preciousness of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.49,0:00:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But also instilled \Nnumerous lessons on how to live.{unsure, lit is "for the sake of living, precepts, numerous left behind"}
